The man then walks over to another counter, where he grabs his salt and pepper shakers, and stirs some salt and pepper into the pan of leeks.
Finally, the man walks over to his cupboard, procures a plate, takes it back to the counter, turns off the stove, picks up the pan and spoons the leeks from the spoon to the plate.
